content:
If you are on FLOWER COLLECTION and it has three checkmarks, go to 1.201. Otherwise, continue reading:

"Not finished yet? Well, that's okay. There's still plenty to do," Etra explains. "If you want to help in some other way, you're more than welcome. What do you say?"

You may replace SUPPLY RUN with FLOWER COLLECTION, or FLOWER COLLECTION with SUPPLY RUN (on your campaign tracker and in the surroundings). Whether or not you do this, discard Etra and each Ranger soothes 2 fatigue.
